<p>British Indian Empire was not entirely governed by the British;</p>
<p>Two prominent parts</p>
<ol>
<li>British India under direct administrative control of the government,</li>
<li>Princely India =(1/3) of the British Empire in India = administered by princes and chiefs.</li></ol>
<p><span style="color:#f1c40f">The war of 1857 marked a tectonic shift in the British perspective towards the princes.</span></p>
